title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2015 - Braunschweig, Germany
description:
After a pause of one year, the JUG Ostfalen is going to host a Coderetreat, again. This time we will try a new nice location in Braunschweig (Brunswick) in Lower Saxony in Germany. 
If you would like to participate, please register at eventbrite (https://www.eventbrite.de/e/global-day-of-coderetreat-2015-braunschweig-tickets-19166287883) (https://www.eventbrite.de/e/global-day-of-coderetreat-2015-braunschweig-tickets-19166287883).
